org.eclipse.papyrus.designer.transformation.library.iconfigurators

Class AnimServiceConfigurator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.papyrus.designer.transformation.library.iconfigurators.AnimServiceConfigurator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IInstanceConfigurator

    public class AnimServiceConfigurator
extends Object
implements IInstanceConfigurator
    Configurator for the Eclipse animation server. This instance is systematically allocated to a node named "Eclipse" call event (for a state machine): it sets the portID attribute of the call event interceptor. The interceptor uses this attribute to initialize the portID attribute within the produced CallEvent data structure.
    Author:
    ansgar
